The TT Score Board Game is a digital scoreboard designed to keep track of points during a table tennis (TT) match. It allows two players to compete while their scores are displayed and updated in real-time. This game is often used for fun practice matches or local tournaments where a simple scoring system is needed.

Key Features:
🎮 Two-player score tracking

⌨️ Keyboard or button controls to increase/decrease scores

🔊 Optional sound effects on score changes

🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Player name inputs

📱 Responsive design for mobile and desktop

🕓 Score history or reset feature (optional)
